fits of dogs in the office', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'working-like-a-dog-benefits-of-dogs-in-the-office-3__trashed', '', '', '2018-04-10 14:25:27', '2018-04-10 14:25:27', '', 0, 'http://localhost/MADS-foodog/wordpress/?p=68', 0, 'post', '', 0),
